# Derek Ji - ELA Portfolio Website

This is a personal ELA portfolio website created for Derek Ji.  
The website showcases reading growth, writing growth, creativity, awards, future goals, and personal achievements throughout the school year.

## Features

- Responsive modern design
- Animated slide sections
- Reading comprehension growth chart
- Favorite texts section
- Academic and creative growth reflections
- Awards and future goals
- Smooth scrolling navigation

## Files Included

- `index.html` → Main website structure
- `style.css` → Website styling and animations
- `script.js` → Interactive JavaScript effects
- `README.md` → Project documentation

## How to Run

1. Download all files.
2. Place them in the same folder.
3. Open `index.html` in your browser.

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Author

Created for Derek Ji's ELA Portfolio.
